  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dca - \u0dba\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One killed in cab-motorcycle collision",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 74-year-old man has died in a car accident yesterday (17th) on the 2nd post of Pelawatta Neluwa main road in the Meghathanna police domain, according to the Meghathanna police.",
        "A 74-year-old man named Pathiranage Somapala, a resident of Galboraluwa, Post 2, died as follows.",
        "The motorcyclist died as a result of the collision between a cab and a motorcycle. Another person traveling on the motorcycle was seriously injured and admitted to the Nagoda hospital.",
        "The driver of the cab, a 24-year-old resident of Wellapanatha, Tanabima, has been arrested by the Meeghathanna police. The Meghathanna police are conducting further investigations."
      ],
